<h3 id='set_health'>: set_health()</h3><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight lua tab-lua"><code><span class="kd">local</span>   <span class="p">;</span><span class="c1">-- example </span>
<span class="p">:</span><span class="n">set_health</span><span class="p">(</span> <span class="mi">100</span> <span class="p">)</span>
</code></pre></div>
<p>Sets the <em>current health</em> for this  to a specific value.</p>
<h4 id='function-call'>Function Call</h4>
<p><code>:set_health( health )</code></p>
<h4 id='parameters'>Parameters</h4>
<p><strong><code>integer</code></strong> <code>health</code><br>
    &emsp;<em>The <strong>new</strong> value you want to set this &#39;s health to.</em></p>
